             was indicted for <rs id="t18020113-46-off253" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18020113-46-off253" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18020113-46-off253" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18020113-46-cd254" type="crimeDate">5th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020113-46-off253 t18020113-46-cd254"></join>, seven mats, value 7s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18020113-46-victim498" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Jenkins
                  <interp inst="t18020113-46-victim498" type="surname" value="Jenkins"></interp>
